following game started a lot of lively discussions in the press in many
countries.} 1... e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. b4 {The Evans Gambit} 4... Bxb4 5.
c3 Bc5 6. O-O d6 7. d4 exd4 8. cxd4 Bb6 9. Nc3 {This simple developing move
