# For a moment Black defends his main weaknesses, but White can bring one more
piece into action.} 30. Bf2 $1 {
Threatens Bh4. Now Black's defence resources are exhausted.} 30... Qb6 31. Nf3
Qxc7 32. Rxc7 Ke8 33. Ng5 Nf8 34. Bc5 Nd7 35. Bd6 {What a strategical triumph!}
