of his extra pawn with} 12. h3 $1 {Then, if 12...} 12... Bxe2 13. Nxe2 cxd5 14.
cxd5 Nxd5 15. O-O {White would conceivably have completed his protracted
development and even emerged a pawn up although, however,Black would still
have retained a measure of the initiative.}) 12... Nxc6 13. Kf1 Rxe2 $1 {
